Atlanta Thrashers Sale May be Completed Tomorrow, Washington Post Reports

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-05-30T22:55:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/atlanta-thrashers-sale-may-be-completed-tomorrow-washington-post-reports.html
The sale of the  Atlanta Thrashers  to
a group that would move the National Hockey League team to
Winnipeg may be completed tomorrow, the Washington Post
reported.  Thrashers owners are in negotiations with True North Sports
and Entertainment, which would relocate the team to  Canada , the
newspaper said.  The  Stanley Cup  final between the  Boston Bruins  and
 Vancouver Canucks  begins June 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  